* Clive &quot;Winston&quot; Blake - bass (1981-1997)
* Hooper
* Djahanshah &quot;P.J.&quot; Aghssa - drums (1981-1983), (2002-2006)
* Mark &quot;Gilly&quot; Gilham - guitars (1983-1989)
* Jonathan &quot;JB&quot; Birch - drums (1983-1989) one-off show in 2022
* &quot;Revvin Kev&quot; - drums (1991-1998)
